  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare the outcomes of Transarterial Chemoembolization (TACE)
      plus Tegafur with TACE alone in patients with intrahepatic cholangiocarcinoma after curative
      resection
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
